history.content:
Hi!


I would personally phase 1 Math 54 because it's important to get a good professor for that class. Between EE16B and CS61C, they both have required labs and somewhat similar enrollment rates so it's up to you which one you'd like to choose. 

However, if you're planning on also taking econ 1, I would recommend using your Phase 1 for that since a lot of Econ/Pre-Haas majors will be looking to take that class as well

Good luck!
Hi, I am planning on tanking math 54, ee16B, cs61c and possibly econ 1. I'm a declared EECS sophomore. Which classes should I phase 1? Any advice would be appreciated!
history.subject: Phase 1
